headline: KeyBank Foundation Announces Awardees of $200,000 CDFI Bicentennial Grants
summary: KeyBank Foundation is proud to announce the recipients of its $5.4MM special grant program designed to strengthen Community Development Financial Institutions (CDFIs). In celebration of KeyBank's (NYSE: KEY) bicentennial, the KeyBank Foundation launched a national grant initiative to support CDFIs across its 27 markets, with a focus on affordable housing and small business growth.
